reviewText: Quite a lot of good information in this DVD.

I was really impressed with the good variety of functional workouts, however it doesn't get 5 stars simply for the fact I had to pay an extra customs charge which I didn't need to pay with the H2H Kettle bell circuits DVD.
This is a great DVD with several routines for developing functional strength.  It is along the lines of Crossfit training and includes many excercises.
